fields.Description:
Required. If this field is set to true,
                Salesforce bypasses workflow rules when it applies the data integration rule;
                otherwise, it applies workflow rules after it applies the rule.

The user license categories that can be assigned the custom permission set
                license. If no user license categories are specified, all users can be assigned the
                license. Possible values include:
                  ${communities}

                  ${communitiesLogin}

                  ${customerCommunities}

                  ${customerCommunitiesLogin}

                  ${internal}

                  ${partnerCommunity}

                  ${partnerCommunityLogin}

                  ${platform}


For more information, see User License Restriction Categories (Developer
                    Preview). This field is available in API version 55.0 and
                later.
